@startuml
title tcu_meter 项目结构 UML

package "core/meter" {
  [main.cpp] as Main
  [meter_process.h/.cpp] as MP
  [dlt645_meter.h/.cpp] as D645
}

package "core/base (reuse)" {
  [BaseProcess] as BP
  [MqttClient] as MC
  [SerialCommunication] as SC
  [ConfigManagerLite] as CFG
  [cJSON] as CJ
}

Main --> MP : 创建/启动进程
MP --|> BP : 继承
MP --> D645 : 轮询读表
MP --> MC : MQTT发布
MP --> CFG : 读取配置
MP --> CJ : 组装JSON
D645 --> SC : 485收发

note right of MP
  核心职责与主流程函数:
  - loadConfig()/initMqtt()/initMeter()
  - pollOnce(): 按枪轮询
  - readGunMeter(): 单枪读取 + 重试
  - publishData()/publishEvent()
end note

note right of D645
  协议职责与主流程函数:
  - readAll(): 总电量/电压/电流
  - readOne()/requestRead()
  - tryExtractFrame()/decodeReadResponse()
  - checksum()/decodeBcdLe()
end note

@enduml
